  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The alchemist can throw bombs that explode with a searing radiance equivalent to that of sunlight and that act as blinding bombs. Undead, fungi, molds, oozes, slimes, and creatures to which sunlight is harmful or unnatural take +2 damage per die from the bomb. Undead that are harmed by sunlight and that fail their saves against the bomb are staggered for 1 round.</p>\n<p>An alchemist must be at least 10th level and must have the blinding bomb discovery before he can select this discovery.</p>",
